description: You know him. You love him. You’ve seen his bare butt on Netflix’s Love. Fresh from our group excursion to the Magic Castle, Kyle Kinane sits that butt down with us to talk about everything from microdosing to robocalls to camping alone in the wilderness. Here’s five words to describe this episode: go marinade yourself in it.
